Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.96,0:00:04.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Deduction flows with\Nthe rhythm of the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.80,0:00:06.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dark stains are rinsed clean and exposed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.85,0:00:08.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The case in the big house
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.44,0:00:10.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Smash with the deductive!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.84,0:00:12.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He sees through the one and only truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.57,0:00:13.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A child in appearance\Nwath the I.Q. of an adult
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.08,0:00:18.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,no case is left unsolved\Nwith Detective Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.94,0:02:01.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, Pops and I are invited by Sonoko\Nand head for her villa in Karuizawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.02,0:02:05.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On our way, our things together\Nwith the car sink into the river
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.69,0:02:07.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when the water level rises.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:09.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We end up being able to spend the night\Nat a house in the remote mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.96,0:02:11.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that we finally manage to get to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.39,0:02:14.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, that night,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.70,0:02:16.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the owner of that house,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:22.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. lwao Akashi dies\Nin has room upstalrs!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.11,0:02:31.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suspicious Spicy Curry" Part 2
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:39.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Yamamura from\Nthe Gunma Prefectural Poltce Station
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.56,0:02:43.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,U,Uh~~excuse me...\NI'd like to ask you a question...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.36,0:02:46.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes...what can I do for you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:52.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are traces of something having\Nbeen wrapped areund your father's wrists
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:55.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea what it could be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:58.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...is that true...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:02.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he had been tied up by someone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.46,0:03:06.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think those are traces of rubber bands...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:12.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father had a habit of bunching everything\Nand anything up with rubber bands,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.34,0:03:15.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and always had rubber bands\Nround both his wrists...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:18.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, just as I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:19.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as you thought...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:20.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.40,0:03:24.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found a lot of rubber bands\Nunder his pillow, so
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.67,0:03:26.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:31.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,ls there any thing else that you recall?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.21,0:03:35.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like having seen someone suspicious\Naround your house,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.74,0:03:37.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,or having heard strange sounds\Nor volces...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:39.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:41.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:43.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.25,0:03:46.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but when I went in front of that room\Nthe first time I heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:49.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the man weeping, "Uuugh..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.19,0:03:51.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.59,0:03:53.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You heard him crying...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:56.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was probably crying\Nafter deciding to commit suicide...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:04:00.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, didn't you see anything else\Nin that room?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.67,0:04:03.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C,Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:05.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be talking...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:08.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,on the floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:12.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think he wiped his mouth with it\Nwhile eating curry,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.91,0:04:14.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because there was a little curry on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:17.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D,Don't tell me that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:20.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If my deduction is correct...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.42,0:04:21.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Agh!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:23.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Akashi didn't go to the dentist...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:27.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason why he was bleeding\Nfrom his mouth was...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:29.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,probably because...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:32.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.07,0:04:33.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, sonny, what's up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.43,0:04:34.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! Hey!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:35.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D,Don't touch!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:37.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:41.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...So, it's just as I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:46.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he had his tooth pulled out
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.81,0:04:50.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,his gums would've started to close\Nlike the not yet opened bud of a flower...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:52.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But his gums are still opened with\Nno signs of closing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:54.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Neither are there signs of blood\Nthat would be
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:57.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in the opening of the gum having\Ndried up or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:05:01.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he just got his tooth pulled out...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:05.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover, the other teeth around it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:08.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This means that whatever\Nhe was clenching with all his mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:10.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,between his teeth was pulled out\Nwith great force...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.67,0:05:13.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get the picture...of this trick!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.28,0:05:15.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.88,0:05:20.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If this trick is what I think it is,\Nat should be somewhere in this room...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:23.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How come it's nowhere in sight...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.29,0:05:25.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.75,0:05:26.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.65,0:05:28.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This half-eaten curry over rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:29.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.79,0:05:33.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, there wasn't any poison in it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.13,0:05:35.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so shall we have them put it away?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.13,0:05:37.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.53,0:05:39.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it'?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.13,0:05:43.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...you want to eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.27,0:05:45.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:49.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H,Hey, stop it!!\NY, You gotta be kidding? Hey, kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.71,0:05:54.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,F,Found it... This is it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:56.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No doubt about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.19,0:05:59.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't that...a tooth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:02.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?\NWhat're you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.89,0:06:04.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What, a human's tooth?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:06.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...Looks like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:08.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No doubt about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.86,0:06:10.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who killed Iwao created
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:12.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,created his own alibi,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:15.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and that person is Hirohito Akashi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:18.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, now that I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:21.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got to get everyone to come here
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:24.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and start the usual\NSleeping Kogoro deduction show!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.85,0:06:27.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,U,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.88,0:06:29.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What shall we do with this tooth...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:30.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.69,0:06:33.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess we better report this\Nto Officer Yamamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:34.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...Right
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.09,0:06:39.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O...Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.26,0:06:41.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:44.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Darn!!...What do I do now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.77,0:06:47.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After I figured out the case and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:51.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't use the voice{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ger to reveal
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.81,0:06:54.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the truth of the case\Nto anyone in this situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:57.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would write but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.38,0:07:00.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but with this sprained wrist I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.32,0:07:03.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only if they'd solve it\Nthemselves somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:06.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My only hope is that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:08.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,(So, what I think is...)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:10.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, with the members here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.69,0:07:15.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan, just where were you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.90,0:07:17.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,(I,I've lost my voice!)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.03,0:07:21.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no?! You mean you lost your voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:27.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were told not to talk because\Nyou'd lose your voice, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.21,0:07:33.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This case is plain to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:38.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the time that Mr. Iwao Akashi\Npassed away in his bedroom
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:41.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,around 7:30 p m. Ran, Conan, Sonoko\Nand Hirohito, who were in this house
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:43.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so we all have an alibi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.59,0:07:48.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was taking a bath, but have no motive
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.56,0:07:51.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and had no way of\Ngetting the rope ready either...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:57.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover...an hour before\Nwe discovered the corpse,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.61,0:07:59.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the light of the bedroom was on,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.77,0:08:01.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but when we discovered the body,\Nit was turned off...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:04.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how you look at\Nit this is suicide!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:07.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,lwao turned off the light of the room
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.68,0:08:10.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and then committed suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.25,0:08:14.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, I'd advise you to stop investigating\Nright now and go on back to the station!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.06,0:08:16.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I,I guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:17.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.79,0:08:19.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is homicide...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.53,0:08:23.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He used a trick to make it look like
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:28.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer is Iwao's adopted son, Hirohito.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.37,0:08:30.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what can I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:32.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without a voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:36.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,how should I accuse him?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:50.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, although\Nthis is going to be a bit bothersome...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:56.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:01.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:04.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan, just what're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.67,0:09:06.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't he gesturing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.24,0:09:10.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ripe crackers...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:17.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,14 pieces of rice crackers?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:18.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,(No, no...)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.52,0:09:20.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Crack, one...four?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.72,0:09:23.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,(Close, close!)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.26,0:09:27.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:29.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,crack code one...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:32.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.83,0:09:35.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Crack this code...once\Nand for all...right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:37.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,(Yes, yes!)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.17,0:09:41.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, what is there to crack?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:44.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:45.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? That curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:47.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong with the curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:50.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was spicy but good
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:51.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.99,0:09:54.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,(No,no)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:56.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh, that's not it...What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.33,0:09:58.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.63,0:09:59.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.09,0:10:01.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hiroto...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.00,0:10:04.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? The old man upstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:05.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A circle?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.10,0:10:07.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.97,0:10:10.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me...3?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:13.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about my age?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:16.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a little over 33 already...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.44,0:10:17.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran was born when I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:20.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about\Nthe amount of curry we all ate?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:24.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hirohito, his father, Sonoko and I\Nhad one serving each,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.69,0:10:26.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but dad ate 3 servings!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.42,0:10:28.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,(Right,right!)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.86,0:10:31.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what's wrong with that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:33.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sure is strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:35.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because you and your group just\Nhappened to come by
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:38.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to this house tonight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.17,0:10:41.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover; Hirohito usually lives here\Nonly wllh hrs father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.30,0:10:43.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are just the two of you here,\Nis that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:44.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:48.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, curry enough for 7 people\Nis a bit too much
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:50.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,for just two people living together,\Ndon't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.85,0:10:52.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would surprise the Indians in India too!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:54.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mentioned it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.58,0:10:56.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.39,0:10:59.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must like curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.19,0:11:04.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I actually love curry too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.79,0:11:05.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.39,0:11:09.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I made quite a lot because\NI usually invite the students
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:12.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that I've become friends, over!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.43,0:11:16.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They really seem to like\Nthe curry I make...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:18.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.51,0:11:20.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Too bad there was nobody\Nat the tennis court today
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:23.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because it rained...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:24.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.05,0:11:33.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tooth...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.95,0:11:34.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,curry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.99,0:11:35.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,no good...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.99,0:11:38.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For the tooth...curry...no good?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:39.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,(Bull's eye!)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:41.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, could it mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.96,0:11:43.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That after a tooth is pulled out,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.23,0:11:46.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,eating something too spicy is not good?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:49.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember when you had\Nyour decayed tooth pulled out,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,0:11:51.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the dentist told you so, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.04,0:11:52.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:55.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, then it's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:57.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You knew that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:12:01.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,your father had his tooth pulled out\N2 or 3 days ago, didn't you, Mr. Akashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.42,0:12:03.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:07.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I had no idea that\Nhe had his tooth pulled out...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:10.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer Yamamura.\Ncould I speak to you for a moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:16.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.26,0:12:18.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.87,0:12:25.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, the coroner is here\Nchecking on the corpse...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:28.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and he says that lwao's tooth seems\Nto have been pulled out
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:30.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,just a while ago, not 2 or 3 days ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:34.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the tooth that was pulled out seems\Nto have been found in the bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.82,0:12:37.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems to have been found for some\Nreason in the half-eaten curry dish...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:42.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There must've been very tough meat\Nin the curry,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.39,0:12:46.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because the teeth near the tooth that had\Ncome off all seemed to be shaky too...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:50.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think such tough meat was in it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:52.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.53,0:12:54.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:56.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.57,0:13:00.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:02.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:04.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he was...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:06.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was eating curry, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.25,0:13:08.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? You want me to sit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:12.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bring the tied part of the necktie\Naround behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:15.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,bring the end of the necktie to the front...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.89,0:13:17.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.49,0:13:19.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:21.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That old man
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:24.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,while biting on the rope!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.93,0:13:25.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,(Bingo!)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.87,0:13:27.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:30.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he would eventually get tired
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:32.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then he'd be strangled!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.14,0:13:37.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His tooth probably flew into the curry\Ndish at that time because of the impact!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.45,0:13:42.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since his mouth is blocked with the rope,\Nhe probably couldn't yell out either!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.35,0:13:45.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean that voice\Nthat I heard back then was
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:48.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,not him weeping, but him groaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:52.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there were no traces\Nof the rope by his mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:54.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's probably because...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.16,0:13:58.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T,The handkerchief!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.70,0:14:00.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember, the handkerchief with\Nthe curry on it was near the corpse,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.40,0:14:02.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember, {The handkerchief with\Nthe curry on r14 was negwthe corpse,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:03.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.97,0:14:06.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was made to bite the handkerchief\Ntogether with the rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.51,0:14:08.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...If so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.98,0:14:12.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then traces of the rope wouldn't be\Nleft around his mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.43,0:14:16.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, his hands weren't tied\Nwhen he was found.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:18.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he grabs the rope with both hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.19,0:14:21.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he can free his mouth\Nso he could've shouted,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.22,0:14:23.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Somebody help!"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:26.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.19,0:14:28.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.50,0:14:31.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bedroom light that was on\Nan hour and a half ago, was turned off
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:34.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when the corpse was found, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:35.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All during that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:39.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,nobody went to that room, so how could\Nthe light have been turned off...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.21,0:14:41.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H,Hey...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:46.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,U,Uh, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:54.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't play around with it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:14:58.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both his wrists were tied with the striimg\Nof the light fixture in a bow tie
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.03,0:15:00.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the edge of the string
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:03.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was connected to the string
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:06.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then when he becomes exhausted
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:08.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the rope will pull away from his mouth,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.00,0:15:11.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,his body will slide down choking his neck,\Nand at the same time
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:14.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the string of the light fixture will be
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.91,0:15:17.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The string that is tied to his wrists will untie...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:22.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the body will be in the exact position\Nas we found at!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.28,0:15:27.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means that the narrow lines that\Nwere found on Mr. Iwao Akashi's wrists
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.49,0:15:29.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,were marks that were left\Nfrom his wrists being tied!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:33.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But these light fixtures have three levels
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.76,0:15:37.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and unless you pull the string 3 times\Nlike Conan just did
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.23,0:15:38.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it won't get dark, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.23,0:15:42.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pulling just once would only turn off\Nthe fluorescent light on the outer part,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:45.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and pulling the string twice will still\Nleave the miniature light on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.87,0:15:47.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Phooey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:51.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the brightness is adjusted to the 2nd\Nlevel and the miniature light is loosened,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.35,0:15:53.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then pulling on the string just once will\Nturn off the light right then and there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:57.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...But, is it possible to untie it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:04.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, this part that is tied to\Nmake the string longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.83,0:16:06.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to tie the hand of someone\Nwho is struggling,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:09.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it would be impossible to do so while the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.06,0:16:13.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, this knot would have to be untied once...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:17.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, this looks to be a complicated knot...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.44,0:16:18.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:21.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T,This is called "Tegusu Musubi!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.11,0:16:23.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.01,0:16:25.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The way a fishing line is tied!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.41,0:16:30.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A slippery line has to be tied like this or\Nit'll get untied!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:34.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!That's why Hirohito's wife went
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:37.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wanted to know how to tie the string\Nof the light fixture firmly in place...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:41.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why was the bedroom string\Ndifferent then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.61,0:16:47.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The string in the bedroom\Nwas tied into a regular knot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:52.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, that's why the string of the light\Nfixture of the bedroom was shorter...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.71,0:16:58.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was unable to untie the knot,\Nso he had to cut it using scissors...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:01.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the string was tied\Ninto a regular knot
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:07.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because the killer didn't know\Nhow to tie it fishing line style!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:10.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right Mr. Hirohito Akashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:18.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The trick you used goes like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.23,0:17:23.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You took the curry to\NIwao's bedroom upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.90,0:17:27.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While he was eating the curry,\Nyou probably covered his mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.28,0:17:30.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,with the handkerchief from behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:33.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and tied him up with the light fixture\Nstring that you cut with the scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:37.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After putting the loop of the rope around\Nhis neck, you made him bite the rope
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.15,0:17:41.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,partway along with the hankerchief,\Nand left him suspended...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.72,0:17:45.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course you threatened him saying
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.23,0:17:48.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that if he lets go of the rope from\Nhis mouth he would choke to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:52.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally all you had to do was tie the\Nstring of the light fixture that both of
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.27,0:17:54.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,his hands were tied with onto the string\Nof the light fixture...and walla!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.64,0:18:00.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you make somebody go to\Nthe bedroom to pick up his curry dish
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.42,0:18:01.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You warn that person saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.94,0:18:05.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the light is on he's still eating\Nso don't go into the room."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.21,0:18:08.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You first ask the person to go get\Nthe plate 10 somewhat minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:10.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,after you bring the curry to his room
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.85,0:18:12.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he most likely is still holding\Nthe rope in has mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.27,0:18:16.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you ask that person to go and\Nget the plate again after a while
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.11,0:18:19.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,goes in and encounters the dead bedy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.51,0:18:23.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since you were with us\Nright through in the living room
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:26.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you most definitely have an alibi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.70,0:18:29.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, are you saying that Hirohito\Nwas at the tennis court
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.30,0:18:33.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in the rain to invite someone\Nto witness his alibi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:38.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He deliberately made curry\Nfor a lot of people...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:40.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O,Oh no..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.85,0:18:43.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means if we didn't come here
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.32,0:18:44.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,this wouldn't have happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:50.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,even if you all didn't come here today,\NI was going to kill him tongiht...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.43,0:18:56.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...It's true that today is the anniversary\Nof my wife's death...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.77,0:19:05.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My wife was found lying on the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.04,0:19:07.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,L,Lying on the ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.94,0:19:08.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.01,0:19:13.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was when I went out to work at a court\Nin Tokyo on a rainy day...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:17.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father suddenly woke my wife\Nwho was asleep with a cold
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.25,0:19:18.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and made her go shopping...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.39,0:19:21.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He told her that\Nhe wanted to eat mushroom rice...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.99,0:19:24.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She should've refused, but she didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.46,0:19:27.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She walked with unsteady steps over to\Na supermarket about 3 kilometers away
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:31.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and on the way back, just as expected,\Nfell to the ground and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.00,0:19:35.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, that's no reason for you to kill him
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:36.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:40.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I decided to kill the day\Nafter my wife's funeral...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.44,0:19:43.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umaware that I was behind him,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:47.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,father was mumbling the following words\Ntowards the altar of my mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:50.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dear...she finally broke down...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:55.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next time I wish he'd get himself\Na healthier wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:58.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A toy that is more durable like Hirohito...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:02.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O...Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:05.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y,You mentioned that\Nyou were adopted...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:10.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. until I heard him say that,\NI believed him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:14.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,thinking that his being selfish was proof
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.74,0:20:18.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that he acknowledged me\Nas his real son...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:22.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...We built a house in the forest\Nand began living here,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.58,0:20:26.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,my father, wife and I, because of\Nmy father's selfishness saying
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:29.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that he wanted to live apart from\Nthe rest of the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:32.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course the same goes for\Nthe string of the light fixture.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.23,0:20:35.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He suddenly lengthened the string\Nof the light fixture of his room
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.26,0:20:37.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and ordered all the strings\Nof the light fixtures
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.56,0:20:39.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in the other rooms to be lengthened
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.10,0:20:42.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? So, the string\Nof the light fixture in that room...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.10,0:20:44.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.37,0:20:47.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,father tied the string in\Nhis room himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.48,0:20:50.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Talk about not knowing\Nhow to tie knots...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.75,0:20:55.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that was a knot...\Nthat my wife had tied...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.18,0:20:59.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't have cut it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.85,0:21:04.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and maybe would've had second\Nthoughts about carrymg out this murder...
