Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.39,0:22:39.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,41! -Righ_1,~,Rc~cr,v1-¢I
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.09,0:22:42.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sure was an uncomfortable case...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.29,0:22:44.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, after all,\Na person passed away so...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.63,0:22:49.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The combination of Sleeping Kogoro and\Ndeduction queen Sonoko,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.50,0:22:51.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,sure can close a case in a jiffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.03,0:22:52.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aaagh!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.07,0:22:55.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I forgot to video tape the deduction show,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.85,0:22:57.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because you started it\Nwuthout going to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.07,0:22:58.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not my problem!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.44,0:23:02.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...I got double tired this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.78,0:23:04.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Ran...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.31,0:23:08.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that I received a call last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.55,0:23:11.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but the number has no caller I.D...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.45,0:23:14.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,if you're talking about the call that came\Nin when you were using the restroom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.06,0:23:16.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he took it...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.62,0:23:19.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a wrong number call...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.99,0:23:20.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S,Shinichi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.23,0:23:24.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that call from Shinichi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.75,0:23:26.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that look on your face,\Nit must've been
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.47,0:23:28.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.90,0:23:29.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.44,0:23:31.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ghads...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.21,0:23:35.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to have worried you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.08,0:23:40.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No more X-size cups for bras'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.53,0:23:42.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,X-size cups means the difference in size
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.55,0:23:45.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,with the under bust is about\N70 centimeters
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.35,0:23:46.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were your breasts that big?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.42,0:23:49.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course not! I'm not a cow, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.93,0:23:54.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...I guess!'ll mail her later...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.47,0:23:59.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,10,000,000 yen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.93,0:24:04.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something about there is someone\Nwho is after the left of her husband
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.04,0:24:07.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and she says if we can nail that person,\Nshe'll pay us 10,000,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.81,0:24:13.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This case would be closed in no time\Nif we use our heads just a little bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.78,0:24:16.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M,Mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.75,0:24:21.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H,Hey, both of you...!
